Interface DependentCallbackAction

CallbackAction, Called<org.apache.wicket.Component>, CriteriaDependent<Object>, Serializable
public interface DependentCallbackAction
extends CallbackAction, CriteriaDependent<Object>

A DependentCallbackAction is an action that depends on a supplied object.

Typically, the caller will redirect to a WebPage built with data from the supplied object
